steps to publish a post in github:

* go to nbellari.github.io/posts folder
* create a markdown and edit it
** When inside the vim, press <F2> in the insert mode to insert the header
* Save the file name with appropriate date
* Do a bundle exec jekyll serve and go to http://localhost:4000 to see the changes
* Once happy with the post, publish with git add, git commit etc.
